data.title: Raja Nazrin dimasyhurkan sebagai Sultan Perak yang baru
data.meta_description:
Raja Nazrin Shah ibni Almarhum Sultan Azlan Shah ditabalkan sebagai Sultan Perak Darul Ridhwan yang ke-35 tepat jam 3.15 petang ini yang membawa kepada gelaran Paduka Seri Sultan Nazrin.

	Pengumuman pelantikan itu diumumkan oleh Orang Kaya Bendahara Seri Maharaja Jen (Bersara) Tan Sri Mohd Zainuddin di sebelah jenazah Almarhum Sultan Azlan Shah...

Bodycam footage shows moments leading to fatal shooting of Victoria Lee by NJ police

Body camera footage released by the New Jersey Attorney General’s Office shows the moments leading up to the fatal shooting of 26-year-old Victoria Lee by police in Fort Lee on July 28. Lee, who had bipolar disorder, was having a crisis when her brother called 911 for medical assistance. Despite emphasizing her mental state and the presence of a small pocket knife, police forcibly entered the apartment at The Pinnacle complex and shot Lee, who had allegedly dropped the knife and was holding a water jug.

Korean American teen dies following alleged assault in LA's K-town

Los Angeles police are investigating the death of 19-year-old Joon Hee Han, who succumbed to a head injury after allegedly being assaulted in Koreatown on July 18. Authorities urge anyone with information to contact the West Bureau Homicide at 213-382-9470.
